Ingredients:

2 slices of bread
Jelly of your choice
Peanut Butter


Directions:
1. Spread jelly on one side of one slice of bread.
2. Spread peanut butter on one side of the other slice of bread.
3. Place one bread on top of the other, so that the peanut butter and jelly fuse. 
4. Sandwich


